stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> active: ingested or created
    
    active --> warm: access frequency drops
    warm --> active: salience boost or recent access
    warm --> cold: prolonged low access
    cold --> warm: renewed relevance
    
    cold --> archived: consolidation recommends
    archived --> warm: explicit restore
    archived --> active: explicit restore with priority
    
    active --> tombstoned: user delete OR known-false detected
    warm --> tombstoned: user delete
    cold --> tombstoned: poisoned source detected
    archived --> tombstoned: explicit suppression
    
    tombstoned --> active: explicit restore<br/>(rare, requires user confirmation)
    
    [*] --> quarantined: low-confidence import OR<br/>malformed source OR<br/>untrusted ingestion
    quarantined --> active: passes review
    quarantined --> tombstoned: review rejects
    
    tombstoned --> deleted: explicit purge<br/>(policy-gated, audit-logged)
    archived --> deleted: explicit purge
    
    deleted --> [*]
    
    note right of active
        Fully available
        Normal retrieval, graph visibility
        ContextPacket eligible
    end note
    
    note right of warm
        Slightly lower default salience
        Still retrievable
        Eligible for summaries
    end note
    
    note right of cold
        Lower default ranking
        Candidate for archive
        Retrievable via explicit search
    end note
    
    note right of archived
        Raw moved to compressed storage
        Archive summary remains active
        Retrieval card searchable
        Graph stub visible
        Full restore possible
    end note
    
    note right of tombstoned
        Excluded from normal retrieval
        Blocks re-insertion of identical content
        Tombstone marker preserved
        Requires explicit restore to re-enable
    end note
    
    note right of quarantined
        Isolated pending review
        Not in normal agent context
        May contain poisoned or low-confidence data
    end note
    
    note left of deleted
        Physical removal where possible
        Minimal deletion audit retained
        Indexes cleaned
        Relationships invalidated
    end note
